Name: Loan Auto-Decision
nFORCE__Description__c: The Loan Auto-Decision Rule context runs when the Auto-Decision Action item is selected from a loan

Name: Credit Request Preprocessing
nFORCE__Description__c: This is run before creating a credit request to determine the parameters for the request

Name: Retrieve Pricing Options
nFORCE__Description__c: Create the pricing option(s) based on information in the Loan.

Name: Filter Pricing Options by DTI
nFORCE__Description__c: Filters the pricing options based on the current max DTI

Name: Proposed Pricing Option
nFORCE__Description__c: Create the proposed pricing option based on information in the loan.

Name: Loan Auto-Policy Exception
nFORCE__Description__c: The Loan Auto-Policy Exception context runs when the Auto-Policy Exception Action item is selected from a loan

Name: CLA Inspection PlaceHolder Creation
nFORCE__Description__c: The CLA Inspection PlaceHolder Creation rule runs when a new Valuation object is created in order to create one or more Document Manager placeholders.
